{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Mozilla 开发者网络 10 周年","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/MDN/At_ten","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>为我们 web 技术的文档化走过 10 年而庆祝！</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"mdn_历史","title":"MDN 历史","isH3":false,"content":"<p>2005 年初，一个理想者组成的小团队建立起来并开始为所有的 Web 开发者提供实时、免费和社区驱动的在线资源.。他们杰出而不寻常的想法逐渐演化成了今天的 Mozilla 开发者网络——一个领先和全面的开放 Web 技术资源库。十年后，我们全球化的社区变得更加的强大，同时，为了能给广泛的网络技术公司提供技术上的支持，我们还坚持编写文档，案例代码 以及学习资源 ，其中就包括像 CSS, HTML, JavaScript 以及各种能够使得网络变得更加强大的东西。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/At_ten/History_of_MDN\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">了解更多 about the history (en-US)</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"为_mdn_做出贡献","title":"为 MDN 做出贡献","isH3":false,"content":"<p>十年来，MDN 社区已经几乎给开放网络贡献了无限多的文档，从最小的字符修改到编写整个一系列新的 API，对开放网络，社区中的每个人都有贡献，每个人既不会付出太多也不会太少。我们已经有超过 90000 页的文档或内容被社区中突出的智谋人（Mozillians）编辑或者被翻译。你将会成为我们中的一员。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Contribute\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">了解更多 about contributing (en-US)</a></p><div class=\"quote\" id=\"sect1\">\n<blockquote>Absolutely invaluable to me in writing my books, <em>The Book of CSS3</em> and <em>The Modern Web</em>. I even gave thanks in the acknowledgements.</blockquote>\n<span class=\"attribution\">— <a href=\"https://twitter.com/stopsatgreen/status/620736175318401024\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Peter Gasston</a></span>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/MDN_at_ten/\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">MDN10 周年</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/At_ten/History_of_MDN\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">MDN 历史 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Contribute\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">为 MDN 贡献 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"MDN 历史","id":"mdn_历史"},{"text":"为 MDN 做出贡献","id":"为_mdn_做出贡献"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"为我们 web 技术的文档化走过 10 年而庆祝！","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"10 Jahre MDN","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"MDN at 10","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MDN en 10","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"MDN a 10 ans","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MDN は 10 周年を迎えました","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MDN at 10","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"10 lat MDN","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"10 anos de MDN","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"10-летие MDN","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"MDN 10 週年","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/mdn/at_ten","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/mdn/at_ten/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/MDN","title":"MDN 项目"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/MDN/At_ten","title":"Mozilla 开发者网络 10 周年"}],"pageTitle":"Mozilla 开发者网络 10 周年 - MDN 项目 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}